      "asbval:target_claim_field": "scope",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "After chromatographic peak detection and feature detection in LC-MS preprocessing, when you have a set of detected features (m/z, retention time, intensity) and need to consolidate redundant or related ion signals into compound-level feature groups before downstream statistical o",
