      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Preprocessing is the crucial first step in analyzing untargeted liquid chromatography\u2013mass spectrometry (LC-MS) or gas chromatography\u2013mass spectrometry (GC-MS) data.",
      "asbval:note": "Logical scope boundary; preprocessing (including alignment) is described as the first step, implying it should not be re-applied to already-aligned data.",
