      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms MsFeatures is used for grouping LC-MS features, but describes it as a 'postanalysis' tool for grouping features representing ions and isotopes of the same compound. The card claims it defines/extends grouping parameter classes for retention-time-based grouping specifically; the paper does not confirm this specific role or parameter-class definition.",
